 />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">A0</span></span>"},{"pid":"02b370374f27ac96c378bf1ddb0b1eb76aec9886","tid":188202,"uid":93547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd22e5ad1342f4d18b0bd8b40cdbdf0b8bc49f0","tid":188202,"uid":103082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:36:28.000Z","msg":"我都係 可能係我睇得佢太重要<br />\n我都想快啲有第二個目標 等我可以真係好好咁放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b608dd8cd23e7d45abadaeb510547d1039d5278b","tid":188202,"uid":66,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n明明係我一廂情願<br />\n人地都冇諗過同我有啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<br />\n但係又諗佢諗到訓唔著"},{"pid":"599654fae1809c7fd32ce0fa474f3e21472a0cfc","tid":188202,"uid":75732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"唉 完全同路人 黎tg傾啦 @playerpp"},{"pid":"a1fff65d3612e05d44b58925ef927faedc945a09","tid":188202,"uid":34680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 完全同路人 黎tg傾啦 @playerpp</blockquote><br />\nplayer點同路法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}